{"tid":1508624,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[多圖注意] Gif文宣圖制作 & 分享","createTime":"2019-08-26T14:42:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T20:34:35.000Z","uid":49575,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"92cf23c15ff303315a65f2c9441875916109e327","tid":1508624,"uid":49575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:42:36.000Z","msg":"身處一個影片世代 我覺得文宣方面都可以做下突破<br />\n有見各巴絲對gif文宣反應唔錯<br />\n所以另外開個post分享下/做紀錄<br />\n做gif既原因最主要想吸引眼球為主 所以太資訊性既文宣應該會避免<br />\n加上動態圖片係網絡上仲未有新一哥出現 依然係gif呢種質素差又mb數大既制式繼續雄霸<br />\n(有見到連登d icon開始用webp 不過普及度唔夠高)<br />\n為顧及各位多數用電話數據睇 已經盡量壓得最細最醜<br />\n如果有巴絲都有意加入就要注意呢點 基本上1X mb左右已經好盡<br />\n制作流程: AE -&gt; 壓片-&gt; 網路gif maker -&gt; 壓圖<br />\n<br />\n過往整過既文宣:<br />\n811<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FuaXnwZ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFuaXnwZ.gif&h=cc4c2f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n824<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OLzWsJ7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOLzWsJ7.gif&h=4a441293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n825<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oo6k5U5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOo6k5U5.gif&h=f111eb38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n91<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港旗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QX2sT4T.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQX2sT4T.gif&h=587d2dde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有如果用緊iphone既可以dl個app叫intoLive<br />\n將gif或者影片變做live photo然後set做動態wallpaper<br />\n效果係咁:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0mPDkLj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0mPDkLj.gif&h=d4054882&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"175e04d6ac1b7b2b63ecbbddb921c05bee5b7550","tid":1508624,"uid":54719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T14:43:57.000Z